1
00:00:49,250 --> 00:00:51,580
The gate to the Myriad Demon Spiritual Realm has opened.

2
00:00:51,580 --> 00:00:54,330
I have waited for you here for a thousand years.

3
00:00:55,120 --> 00:00:56,330
My name is Lingxi.

4
00:00:57,040 --> 00:00:59,870
A thousand years ago, you used the power of salvation

5
00:00:59,870 --> 00:01:02,200
to save the entire Fox Clan.

6
00:01:02,450 --> 00:01:04,180
My memory is still incomplete,

7
00:01:04,660 --> 00:01:06,660
so I don't recall what you're talking about.

8
00:01:06,660 --> 00:01:08,500
You may not know this, Master of the Lamp.

9
00:01:08,500 --> 00:01:12,500
Your lost memories are right here in the Myriad Demon Spiritual Realm.

10
00:01:16,950 --> 00:01:18,160
We will go together.

11
00:01:24,660 --> 00:01:25,660
And me.

12
00:01:26,950 --> 00:01:27,870
I'll go too.

13
00:01:28,450 --> 00:01:30,450
Don't push yourself, Qinghe.

14
00:01:30,700 --> 00:01:33,300
The Valley Master is waiting to be laid to rest,

15
00:01:35,289 --> 00:01:36,500
and they need help here.

16
00:01:36,500 --> 00:01:37,750
We will be back soon.

17
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:40,750
Okay, make sure to come back safely.

18
00:01:42,950 --> 00:01:43,750
Everyone.

19
00:01:44,200 --> 00:01:46,080
The gate to the Spiritual Realm has opened.

20
00:01:46,080 --> 00:01:48,200
Follow me into the Spiritual Realm.

21
00:02:06,330 --> 00:02:09,160
How impudent. The Master of the Ferrying Lamp is here in person,

22
00:02:09,160 --> 00:02:11,039
why don't you show yourselves?

23
00:02:11,160 --> 00:02:12,500
Forgive us, Master of the Lamp.

24
00:02:12,500 --> 00:02:15,330
A thousand years ago, the Spiritual Realm was infected by evil spirits,

25
00:02:15,330 --> 00:02:17,500
and the Master of Shadows was consumed by malice,

26
00:02:17,500 --> 00:02:19,160
accidentally injuring the Demon Clan.

27
00:02:19,160 --> 00:02:20,910
Seeing the Master of Shadows here today

28
00:02:20,910 --> 00:02:22,000
made us wary.

29
00:02:27,120 --> 00:02:29,829
Everyone, regarding the misunderstanding from a thousand years ago,

30
00:02:29,829 --> 00:02:32,450
I will definitely give you an explanation today.

31
00:02:32,450 --> 00:02:35,040
This trip is only for the truth of the Creation Shrine,

32
00:02:35,040 --> 00:02:38,770
I have no intention of disturbing the peace of the Spiritual Realm.

33
00:02:45,500 --> 00:02:47,160
Hey, Master of the Lamp,

34
00:02:47,910 --> 00:02:50,410
they won't make a rash move for now.

35
00:03:22,950 --> 00:03:26,950
Master of the Lamp, this is the Divine Stone of Truth left by the Creator.

36
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:29,410
As long as you place your hand on the Divine Stone,

37
00:03:29,410 --> 00:03:32,910
all your sealed memories will flood back.

38
00:04:46,830 --> 00:04:49,000
In my name of Creation,

39
00:04:49,830 --> 00:04:52,080
I sentence you to eternal destruction.

40
00:05:18,500 --> 00:05:20,430
Don't be afraid, Sister. I'm here.

41
00:05:28,500 --> 00:05:30,660
Why are you crying? I'm fine, aren't I?

42
00:05:34,700 --> 00:05:37,120
Oh no, they're evil spirits from the previous epoch.

43
00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:38,500
They have broken through the seal.
